title: Introduction to the Ninja Coffee Bar™
description:
Choose a Size, Choose a Brew—the Ninja Coffee Bar is the best coffeehouse in town right on your counter.

Learn more about the Ninja Coffee Bar™ at http://www.ninjacoffeebar.com. 

Get recipes for your Ninja Coffee Bar at http://www.ninjakitchen.com/recipes.
